Install puppet-lint
    $ apt-get install -y ruby
    $ gem install puppet-lint -v 2.1.1
lets install tmux for debugging:
    $ sudo apt-get install tmux
start tmux
    $ tmux
getting appache pid and strace to see what it's doing when it crashes
    $ ps aux | grep apache
    $ sudo strace -p pid
    $ kill tmux-session
